title: Ebro In The Morning - Ebro Goes Off + Someone Farted In The Uber

Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/18/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about Ye's continuous nonsense, one member of the team farts in an Uber, and much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
